text: Marzhan Akzhigit (born 29 June 2000) is a Kazakhstani freestyle skier. She competed in the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Freestyle skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Kazakhstani female freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of Kazakhstan
